---
import hands from '../../assets/holding-hands.jpeg'
---

<section id="about" class="flex justify-evenly py-10 px-2 bg-green-400">
  <article
    class="relative h-80 w-full justify-center flex text-center items-center"
  >
    <img
      src={hands}
      alt="Veronica Crespo"
      class="h-4 w-4 rounded-sm shadow-md"
    />
    <h4 class="max-w-lg text-2xl text-white z-10 text-ellipsis">
      "El amor, el apoyo y la amabilidad vienen como regalos con envoltura de
      esperanza"
    </h4>
  </article>
</section>
